snippet.title: Robot Dinosaurs that Shoot Beams When They Roar
snippet.description: Robot Dinosaurs that Shoot Beams When They Roar Side scrolling action shooter with a crazy story line. ROAARRR!

snippet.title: Me and My Dinosaur
snippet.description: Me and My Dinosaur Escape the greedy scientists and angry humans to find the real paradise for you and your dinosaur.

snippet.title: T-Rex Rampage: Prehistoric Pizza
snippet.description: T-Rex Rampage: Prehistoric Pizza Play a hungry T-Rex dino. Destroy the city and find slices of pizza to survive.

snippet.title: Dinosaurs and Meteors
snippet.description: Dinosaurs and Meteors Use the skills of the dinosaurs to prevent destruction of planet earth by meteors.

snippet.title: Bamboo Dino
snippet.description: Bamboo Dino Action game. Help the dino to retrieve his eggs defeating the enemies in each of the levels.

snippet.title: Hunga Hatch
snippet.description: Hunga Hatch Click on the hatched dinosaurs of groups of three or more to remove them.

snippet.title: Dino Run
snippet.description: Dino Run Run as fast as you can and try to escape the wall of doom to save the dinosaurs from extinction.

snippet.title: Urban Brawl
snippet.description: Urban Brawl Fight off zombies, bunnies, dinosaurs, and UFOs with your handy golf club and pistol. No suburbanites allowed.
